 'yoga_pilates', 'extension', array['yoga_mat'], 'beginner', false,
 'Lie on your back. Slide hands under the thighs or buttocks. Press elbows into the floor, arch the back, and lower the crown of the head to the floor gently. The back is arched, chest is open. Hold 1-2 minutes.',
