 'yoga_pilates', 'stretch', array['yoga_mat'], 'advanced', false,
 'From a low lunge, begin to slide the front leg forward and the back leg back. Use blocks under the hands if the hips don''t reach the floor. Hold for 1-3 minutes each side. The front leg is straight, back leg extends behind.',
