 'yoga_pilates', 'stretch', array['yoga_mat'], 'intermediate', false,
 'From a low lunge, walk the front foot to the outside of the hand. Lower the back knee to the floor. Walk both hands inside the front foot. Option: lower onto the forearms. Hold 1-3 minutes each side.',
 'Not placing the front foot to the outside of the hand (foot inside the hand reduces the hip-opening stretch), rushing to the forearms before the hips are ready (hands on blocks is perfect).',
