 'Lie on back, feet on a wall or resistance band loop at hip height. Press through parallel feet (10 reps) → heels together toes apart — Pilates V position (10 reps) → toes together heels apart (10 reps) → single heel raises (10 each). Maintain neutral pelvis throughout.',
