 'Sit with legs straight, one ankle crossed over the other. Roll back with legs overhead (rollover). Separate legs, switch the cross, roll back up. Teaser position at the top (legs at 45°, arms forward). Circle arms back and clasp hands. Lower legs. Dive forward. Repeat.',
 'Rushing any part of the sequence (each element must be controlled), kicking into the rollover instead of articulating, attempting this without mastering its component exercises (teaser, rollover, roll-up) first.',
