 array['Boomerang components: rollover → switch cross → roll up to teaser → circle arms → forward fold — each is a discrete skill','This is considered one of the most advanced mat exercises in classical Pilates: master every component before combining','The breath changes with each phase: learn the breath pattern before adding the complexity of the movement','The ''Advanced'' classification in the classical Pilates sequence places this near the end of the full mat workout for a reason'],
