 'stretching',
 array['Push the knee away: the opposite hand pushes the crossed knee away from the body — this externally rotates the hip and targets the gluteal muscles specifically','Then pull toward the chest: after pushing the knee away, pull the bottom leg toward the chest to increase the intensity','This is the most accessible glute stretch: lying down makes it appropriate for anyone who cannot do pigeon pose','The glutes are the largest muscle in the body and the most commonly tight in desk workers: stretching them daily prevents lower back pain and hip stiffness'],
